data.name: Egg Dee - Sanjay Omelette
data.description: Sanjay Omelette is a place in Jaipur which is serving the best egg dishes ever made from 1981 ,From older generation to the younger ones. Sanjay Omelet is an unique takeaway omelette place. They have at least 120 varieties of very unique omelets. One of their most famous is the Omelette Pizza and butter Masala Omelette. The spices and preparation is done by some secret recipe and the taste is so unique that every day from 11AM to 11PM there are at least 150-200 locals who eat here. They've also started there dine in setup at the same place, which is the first ever EGG theme based Restaurant in India. This is a unique place and the owner Mr. Sanjay was also one of the participants at Master-chef India season 1, and got selected Because of his unique omelet. This hidden gem should be introduced to travelers!
